    <para id="id264307">By setting the derivative to zero and solving for <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>λ</m:mi></m:math>, one can show that the optimal <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>λ</m:mi></m:math> is</para>
    <equation id="id264332">
